{"id":243882,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-江苏启东民众抗议信息遭屏蔽，网友被拘/","date":"2012-07-30T09:31:24Z","modified":"2012-12-30T16:56:55Z","title":"维权网 | 江苏启东民众抗议信息遭屏蔽，网友被拘留（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2hBowk-KIz0/UBZJu8Sa5ZI/AAAAAAAAKQA/4P5LCh5-Wf4/s1600/%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E6%88%B4%E5%AE%9D%E5%81%A5%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B.jpg.jpg\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'> </a><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2hBowk-KIz0/UBZJu8Sa5ZI/AAAAAAAAKQA/4P5LCh5-Wf4/s320/%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E6%88%B4%E5%AE%9D%E5%81%A5%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B.jpg.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>感谢南通戴宝健提供的现场图片</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方斌报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，江苏省启东市数万居民上街抗议日本王子纸业向启东附近海域排污项目，居民冲进了市政府，警方与民众对峙，现场发生冲突。当天南通市政府发布公告决定永久取消王子企业排海项目。然而当晚，武警却陆续进入启东市，并伴有电子信号干扰车。同时，网友通过微博发布的现场消息被屏蔽，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日，一名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span><span>后孙性女网友因发布现场消息被行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天并被处罚款</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>元。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本网信息员在百度上搜索“启东”时，有关民众游行抗议及日本王子纸业的相关信息已不复存在，搜索此前网易网站的《江苏启东民众游行抗议批准日本造纸厂建设》的报道提示为“无法显示网页”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-cgBVvssNepo/UBZKfLCTF9I/AAAAAAAAKQI/-KIdcSCuI7k/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE0011.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"72\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-cgBVvssNepo/UBZKfLCTF9I/AAAAAAAAKQI/-KIdcSCuI7k/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE0011.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>网络截图</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-XjKcpNcgHcE/UBZKpHsQ8_I/AAAAAAAAKQQ/Ogd--nAl100/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"165\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-XjKcpNcgHcE/UBZKpHsQ8_I/AAAAAAAAKQQ/Ogd--nAl100/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xuJMYH79XbU/UBZKyMA9NqI/AAAAAAAAKQY/7kC50R726tM/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"149\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xuJMYH79XbU/UBZKyMA9NqI/AAAAAAAAKQY/7kC50R726tM/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因担忧王子纸业的排污工程会破坏自己和子孙的生存环境，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>启东民众向市公安局递交了游行申请书，然而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日公安局以“集会地为人员密集的公共场所”为由不予批准民众的游行申请。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日，大、中在校学生被要求在承诺书上签名，承诺书中指“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日在启东永安广场进行的抵制南通大型达标水排海工程的集会游行为非法活动，如有参与，会受到相应治安处罚，将直接影响进行高校学习深造，乃至影响个人前途命运”，很多学生被迫签下“我坚决做到不组织、不参与、不支持、不围观”的承诺书。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HvU4BMvQ_n8/UBZL4nx6E9I/AAAAAAAAKQg/xiNQvzXfsxc/s1600/000.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HvU4BMvQ_n8/UBZL4nx6E9I/AAAAAAAAKQg/xiNQvzXfsxc/s320/000.jpg\" width=\"250\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DhUz1_PGpWQ/UBZMCaC5NaI/AAAAAAAAKQo/SKF3ZW9mYB0/s1600/111.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DhUz1_PGpWQ/UBZMCaC5NaI/AAAAAAAAKQo/SKF3ZW9mYB0/s320/111.jpg\" width=\"302\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-lzcbt5h9ii0/UBZMNDPYZtI/AAAAAAAAKQw/9cfwWy7miEI/s1600/70d2223ebd5jw1dvcmrhtzutj.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-lzcbt5h9ii0/UBZMNDPYZtI/AAAAAAAAKQw/9cfwWy7miEI/s320/70d2223ebd5jw1dvcmrhtzutj.jpg\" width=\"310\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>启东当局压制民意，对民众的呼声置若罔闻的作法，没能阻止住大规模的游行抗议行动。虽然最终当地政府承诺永久取消排海项目工程，但因为孙性网友被拘留的现实，一些维权界人士担忧，政府会对参与抗议、围观行动，发布现场消息的启东民众和网友们进行“秋后算账”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2443117578439486547?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,20175,19196]}